subject: Hello
body:
Hello
It's my pleasure contacting you.
I am looking to work with you to guide me to purchase good properties/luckup shops for leasing out in your country with the money my late parents left behind. Both died in a fatal accident. Any other profitable venture you know of in your country will be welcomed please.
You will be highly rewarded monetarily for your kind help. US$20M is for this purpose.
Endeavor to contact me immediately for more detailed information.
Regards,
Miyenko Chenko.

subject: Re: Hello
body:
Hello Miyenko Chenko,

Thank you for reaching out to me. I'm sorry to hear about the loss of your parents in a fatal accident. It must be a difficult time for you. I would be happy to help guide you in purchasing properties or exploring other profitable ventures in my country.

Could you please provide me with more details about the type of properties you are interested in and the specific location? Additionally, it would be helpful to know what kind of budget you have in mind for these investments.

Once I have more information, I can assist you further and provide any guidance or suggestions that might be beneficial. Looking forward to hearing from you soon.

Best wishes,
Peggy

subject: Re: Hello
body:
Hello Peggy,

Sorry for my late response.

I will suggest you look out properties for me in your city and in an

Kindly get back to me so we will discuss all other details accordingly.

Kind regards,

Miyenko Chenko.

subject: Re: Hello
body:
Hello Miyenko Chenko,

Thank you for reaching out to me. I appreciate your interest in investing in properties in my city. Could you please provide me with more details about the type of property you are looking for? Are you interested in residential or commercial properties? Any specific location preferences?

Also, it would be helpful to know what kind of businesses you are planning to venture into once you relocate to my country. Are there any particular industries or sectors that interest you?

I look forward to hearing back from you and discussing further details.

Best wishes,
Peggy
